<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>As @user3429660 advice you use jquery  autocomplete. </p>

<p>Create a function who call a webservice that you have defined in your nodejs with express for example. the web service return data in JSON to the function and the view is updated with jquery</p>
    </div>
